Hello Everyone !! 
I am here to introduce you to a new way to send WhatsApp messages using the pywhatkit module. 
The code is shown below:- 
pwk.sendwhatmsg("number_you_want_to_text","your_message", hour, min).
Make sure the hour is in 24-hour format. 
